堆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8659a58ac6c20f2f9a52df4dbb2891a5aee1bd","tid":760860,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"同學仔個阿爺隨時後生過佢老竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9af71db99c5845af0a2767b02ca8ecbbaaf2ba","tid":760860,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"個細路係依兩公婆個仔既女呀?<br />\n<br />\n痴線,六十幾歲都仲生?"},{"pid":"351426aff99b07868e8552db3efcabb778385ad6","tid":760860,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7573f4a113935d60c546dfbca2d666716d8d7d5","tid":760860,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9af71db99c5845af0a2767b02ca8ecbbaaf2ba","tid":760860,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"個細路係依兩公婆個仔既女呀?<br />\n<br />\n痴線,六十幾歲都仲生?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"一個唔覺意嫁到有錢仔帶契全家 當搏一搏"},{"pid":"00c7fa645e3c2c036b5a61fd4f9b015b0ea0d868","tid":760860,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"又係返大陸娶老婆個D?<br />\n都唔知個女係咪佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaf807ca5ed3dced9a05ff53910136cdb9def91","tid":760860,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98f08ecc7665eba9bc93d19ee48f09e7d251f201","tid":760860,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/102340_f9fe4e063592900b10881737466079b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F102340_f9fe4e063592900b10881737466079b3.png&h=6ff5343b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/